<h3>Description</h3>
<p>Adds a custom emulator param for this file/project. It's sometimes useful to be able to specify
a specific emulator param for your program, without the hassle of having to change things manually in the TRSE settings.
<p>
This method will add an emulator parameter on ctrl+R, but will not change any of the TRSE settings.

<code>
// Adds the "-nothrottle" command to the MAME emulator
@addemulatorparam "-nothrottle"
</code>
